{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 8(b) shows the energy-delay product (EDP), the associated area, and the cost for the 3D system with above-mentioned NoC configurations.",
    "We employ EDP as the NoC performance evaluation metric since it captures both performance and energy in a single term.",
    "From Fig. 8(b), we observe that integrating additional TSV links to a mesh NoC leads to EDP improvement by 12% but also results in an increase in area by 16% and cost by 35.5%.",
    "In contrast, the NoC in Atleus significantly outperforms the baseline mesh with a minimal increase in area.",
    "Specifically, we observe a 27% reduction in EDP with only a 4% increase in the NoC area and a 7.5% increase in cost."
  ]
}